Content:: Kobe Goossens (born 29 April 1996) is a Belgian cyclist, who currently rides for UCI WorldTeam Intermarché–Wanty–Gobert Matériaux.[3] In October 2020, he was named in the startlist for the 2020 Vuelta a España.[4] This biographical article related to a Belgian cyclist born in the 1990s is a stub.
